        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Returning Inappropriate Cash Handouts Act or the RICH Act</b></p> <p>This bill excludes individuals with adjusted gross income equal to or greater than $1 million from panedmic unemployment assistance and additional benefits under federal pandemic unemployment compensation.</p>]]></text>
